com.paypal.merchant.sdk.domain

Interface TransactionRecord

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public interface TransactionRecord
extends java.io.Serializable
    This class represents a historical transaction. Perhaps a payment or refund that happened yesterday, last week, or just a moment ago.
